text: Quiet, cosy, convenient. Friendly condo manager, gardener and security guard.Security guard always wave at us.Love this place!
Great location. Quiet despite walking distance from MRT. Timeless design. Near great schools. Perfect for family.
Very good neighborhood. Quiet and peaceful. Looks safe and the people are nice.
Visitors parking lots very little only 8lots for the 2 blocks.
Went to collect back a bcr machine.
